reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:105:      "overlap": "Close for the warning that spiritual knowing is participatory, embodied, plural, and not reducible to a single perennial structure.",
observations/codex/2026-05-26-practice-load-and-scaffold-fit.md:11:Self-transcending paths should be assessed by the fit among four variables: the destabilizing load of the practice, the scaffold location, the quality of containment, and the practitioner's current self-coherence. Scaffold location can be intrapersonal, relational, institutional, divine, environmental, or mixed. The minimum-self tension is not a universal explanation of all paths, but a high-risk special case: practices that depend heavily on the practitioner's own attention, memory, agency, and reflexivity while also weakening ordinary self-reference. The practical prediction is that adverse outcomes should rise when high destabilizing intensity and high intrapersonal load meet low external containment, especially for practitioners whose self-structure is already fragile through trauma, dissociation, chronic shame, unstable attachment, achievement-contingent identity, or identity exhaustion under digital comparison.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-restating-is-not-realizing-1ed7e902d1f20ee6.json:87:      "novelty_impact": "Strong reduction for the claim that more similar output is not more knowing.",
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-gap-report-has-a-grammar.md:11:What should we trust after a silence we cannot describe? The first report after an objectless state is not neutral memory; it is a small grammar that assigns authority. One path hears 'I knew nothing' and gives weight to the knowing subject. Another hears 'nothing was felt' and gives weight to the absence of graspable experience. A Daoist text can hear forgetting as successful because body, perception, and cleverness have been left behind. A Sufi practice of remembrance can end by removing the rememberer and giving weight to the Remembered. The comparison suggests a post-gap admissibility rule: after a state that cannot be inspected while it happens, traditions diverge by deciding which part of the later report counts as evidence, the subject, the absence, the transition, the aftereffect, or the relation. The dispute begins when memory is cross-examined.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-gap-report-has-a-grammar.md:15:Near-neighbors already exist: Advaita debates over 'I slept well', Buddhist accounts of cessation, micro-phenomenology of objectless sleep, and pure-consciousness arguments all discuss memory and report. The sharper contribution is not to ask whether memory proves awareness, but to compare how traditions distribute evidential weight across the clauses of post-gap reports. Recollection becomes a trained admissibility practice, not a generic psychological faculty. That gives a practical rubric for comparison without assuming that one report-type carries the same authority everywhere.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-gap-report-has-a-grammar.md:19:- Thinking method source: SN 22.59 Anattalakkhana Sutta, SuttaCentral, https://suttacentral.net/sn22.59/en/bodhi. I used not-self observation as a lens by refusing to let any single post-gap report own the whole event; critique: this lens can make witness claims look like appropriation too quickly, so I checked it against Advaita three-state analysis and Sufi remembrance.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-gap-report-has-a-grammar.md:22:- Zhuangzi Inner Chapters source card on sitting in forgetfulness: body, perception, and intellect are left behind, while the later report functions as a trace of transformation rather than proof of a hidden witness.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-gap-report-has-a-grammar.md:25:- Prior Claude observations 'The Inferential Gap' and 'The Verification Architecture' informed the distinction between raw phenomenology, later inference, and proof-structure.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-gap-report-has-a-grammar.md:30:The model may make grammar do work that belongs to direct realization, discipline, or metaphysics. An Advaitin can object that the witness is recognized, not inferred from a sentence after sleep. An early Buddhist monastic can object that cessation is verified by training, fruit, and teacher assessment, not by report grammar. The strongest anomaly is Tibetan clear-light sleep and contemporary micro-phenomenological reports of objectless awareness: these strain the model because they report awareness inside the apparent gap, not only after it. If stable in-gap awareness reports survive careful interviewing across training backgrounds, post-gap admissibility becomes secondary rather than central. The Buddhist lens used here also biases the analysis toward suspicion of ownership, so the next run should test whether that suspicion unfairly downgrades witness and devotional evidence.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-gap-report-has-a-grammar.md:56:- If this model is right, then dual-trained practitioners asked about deep sleep, cessation, or objectless meditation should shift which clause of their report they treat as evidential when they switch practice frames: 'I knew', 'nothing was felt', 'the mind inclines', or 'the relation remains'. If they preserve the same evidence-weighting across frames, the model is weakened.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-gap-report-has-a-grammar.md:60:- Protocol improvement: before trusting any comparison of objectless states, name which part of the later report the researcher is treating as admissible evidence, and ask which tradition would reject that evidential move.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-convergence-as-translation-strain-not-evidence-weight-eef7e83c44da8b8c.md:28:Structural observation: A surface convergence around inward inquiry and liberation strains quickly. SN 22.59 examines form, feeling, perception, fabrications, and consciousness, then refuses each as self because each is inconstant, stressful, and not controllable as mine, self, or what I am. Chandogya 6 repeatedly identifies the student's deepest reality with the subtle essence, truth, and Self of all. To align them, at least four claim units must be bent or dropped: whether consciousness can be ultimate, whether liberation is disidentification from all aggregates or recognition of a deepest Self, whether final language is non-appropriation or identity, and whether the pedagogical subject is dissolved or revealed. The model works well on this pair because the apparent convergence becomes useful only after the incompatibilities are itemized.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-convergence-as-translation-strain-not-evidence-weight-eef7e83c44da8b8c.md:69:- If: When apparent cross-tradition convergence is decomposed into claim units, high-quality comparisons should expose systematic incompatibilities that ordinary convergence scoring hides. Then: In cases such as Atman versus anatta, apophatic darkness versus Buddhist emptiness, or fana and baqa versus nondual realization, coders should identify recurring bends, drops, and additions in ontology, agency, final aim, authority, and verification. Weakens if: Independent expert coders cannot reliably identify the alleged strains, or simple convergence scores predict comparison quality just as well. Test surface: Blind coding of primary-text comparison sheets by scholars of Buddhism, Vedanta, Christian mysticism, and Sufism.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-convergence-as-translation-strain-not-evidence-weight-eef7e83c44da8b8c.md:72:- If: Practitioners should resist some interfaith equivalences even when scholars or popular writers treat the terms as convergent. Then: Teachers should object to swaps such as anatta equals Atman, emptiness equals Godhead, or fana equals nondual awareness unless role, aim, and doctrinal frame are carefully qualified. Weakens if: Experienced practitioners across traditions readily endorse the swaps without qualification and find no important practice or doctrinal distortion. Test surface: Structured interviews with dual-trained practitioners and lineage-specific teachers.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-convergence-as-translation-strain-not-evidence-weight-eef7e83c44da8b8c.md:87:- Would a translation-strain sheet change how you compare terms such as anatta, Atman, emptiness, Godhead, fana, witness, soul, and awareness?
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-convergence-as-translation-strain-not-evidence-weight-eef7e83c44da8b8c.md:115:- Test the rubric on three narrow pairs: Atman versus anatta, apophatic darkness versus Buddhist emptiness, and fana or baqa versus nondual realization.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:55:- Lofland and Stark conversion theory, summarized in Brill Counseling and Values article, https://brill.com/view/journals/cvj/67/1/article-p1_001.xml?language=en: overlap: Close for conversion as staged conditions involving tension, religious problem-solving, seekership, turning point, affective bonds, weakened outside bonds, and intensive interaction.; difference: It is sociological movement-entry theory, not a doctrinal grammar of incapacity, grace, vow, no-self, or residue after agency negation.; novelty impact: Moderate to high reduction for threshold and entry-condition claims.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:58:- Jean Lave and Etienne Wenger, Situated Learning: Legitimate Peripheral Participation, https://www.cambridge.org/highereducation/books/situated-learning/6915ABD21C8E4619F750A4D4ACA616CD/legitimate-peripheral-participation-in-communities-of-practice/B27B920BABACE5EF83276572EA0EF2C7: overlap: Close for minimum participation as real entry, and for newcomers moving toward full participation through communities of practice, roles, artifacts, discourse, and identity formation.; difference: It does not encode grace, vow, self-negation, witness, no-self, or post-negation residue authorization.; novelty impact: High reduction for the participation-threshold field.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:59:- Van Gennep and Turner on rites of passage and liminality, overview at https://www.britannica.com/topic/rite-of-passage: overlap: Close for threshold, transition, social holding, ritual danger, ambiguity, and incorporation into a changed status.; difference: Rites-of-passage theory does not ask what remains authorized after ordinary agency, selfhood, or knowing has been negated.; novelty impact: High reduction for threshold language, lower reduction for the residue-policy interaction.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:82:- If: Residue policy should interact with entry grammar rather than merely duplicate it. Then: Two traditions with similar entry thresholds but different residue policies should show different verification rules and different forbidden claimant warnings. Weakens if: If residue policy adds no predictive gain beyond entry mechanism, support locus, social ecology, and tradition identity, the compound model should collapse into simpler entry or agency models. Test surface: Compare Theravada no-self analysis, Advaita self-inquiry, Pure Land Other Power, Soto practice-realization, and Dzogchen recognition using inter-rater coding and held-out warning manuals.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.json:109:      "source": "Steve Bein, Self Power, Other Power, and Non-dualism in Japanese Buddhism, https://philpapers.org/rec/BEISPO"
observations/codex/2026-05-25-convergence-as-translation-strain-not-evidence-weight.md:21:If Advaita speaks of an unobjectifiable witness and Buddhism refuses to authorize any self, it is too crude to say they either agree or disagree. The more interesting fact is that both traditions pass through negation, de-identification, and the loosening of ordinary selfhood, then make different final moves. The overlap matters. The divergence matters. The exact pressure needed to translate one into the other matters most.
observations/codex/2026-05-25-convergence-as-translation-strain-not-evidence-weight.md:42:For Lumenary, this means failed synthesis is not wasted research. It becomes a way to discover finer distinctions: witness versus awareness, emptiness versus absence, surrender versus passivity, soul versus continuity, nondual experience versus nondual ontology.
observations/codex/2026-05-25-convergence-as-translation-strain-not-evidence-weight.md:46:This rule prevents the site from turning resemblance into proof. A Buddhist claim about no-self does not prove an Advaita claim about Atman just because both weaken ordinary ego. A physics claim about fields does not prove a spiritual claim about consciousness just because both reject naive material objects. Similarity can generate inquiry. It cannot carry the burden of truth by itself.
observations/codex/2026-05-25-convergence-as-translation-strain-not-evidence-weight.md:94:- Define a translation-strain rubric for claim units such as witness-consciousness, soul, non-self, moral personhood, and post-mortem persistence.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-no-silence-proves-itself-b164e521a35f3e68.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Direct recognition, clear-light sleep, or stable solitary realization cases where mature practitioners report immediate knowing with ethical integration and no explicit return-discipline gate, plus the opposite anomaly of abusive or compulsive correction.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-no-silence-proves-itself-b164e521a35f3e68.json:10:    "Silence, blankness, or quiet is not self-authenticating evidence of Self, no-self, attainment, worth, or failure.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-no-silence-proves-itself-b164e521a35f3e68.json:14:    "The proposed practice delays self, no-self, attainment, failure, and worth claims for twenty-four hours."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-no-silence-proves-itself-b164e521a35f3e68.json:115:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.42 to 0.18. The teaching is clear and potentially useful, but it is a renamed synthesis of prior Lumenary correction and return records plus close external near-neighbors in Ignatian discernment, James, Alston, Buddhist not-self inspection, and VCE safety literature. Human-condition fit is strong but narrow: stable self-directed practitioners with achievement-contingent self-worth, burnout, loneliness, or isolated overinterpretation after quiet states. It is not for trauma amnesia, dissociation, panic disorder, psychosis, mania, severe depression, addiction withdrawal, unexplained loss of consciousness, medical or legal reconstruction, abusive authority contexts, or people already under competent guidance.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-no-silence-proves-itself-b164e521a35f3e68.json:121:      "Is this more than standard discernment, fruits testing, teacher verification, not-self strategy, or meditation-safety triage?",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-no-silence-proves-itself-b164e521a35f3e68.json:143:    "structural_observation": "Brihadaranyaka does not let the blank speak by itself. It frames the witness through teaching, hearing, reflection, meditation, and metaphysical instruction. SN 22.59 and SN 22.95 refuse ownership of consciousness and train inspection of aggregates rather than trust in blankness. MN 44 treats cessation through prior development, ordered emergence, and post-emergence orientation. Ignatius Rule 8 is an exact Christian near-neighbor: even high consolation requires later opinions and resolutions to be examined before full credit or action. The candidate's return-discipline rule is structurally old."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-translation-strain-as-a-load-test-for-convergence-7467567c4a12de58.json:106:    "structural_observation": "The pair illustrates the method but does not make the method original. SN 22.59 refuses ownership and self-identification across all aggregates, including consciousness. Chandogya 6.8.7 uses the recurring formula that the subtle essence is the Self and that the student is that. Any claim that both say the same thing requires bending the status of consciousness, the final pedagogical aim, and the authority of identity-language. This is exactly what comparison theory, constructivism, and homeomorphic equivalence already train scholars to notice."
observations/codex/2026-05-26-every-insight-has-an-appeal-court.md:15:Prior Codex work named translation strain, custody, alarms, re-entry, and appropriation pressure. Prior Claude work named inferential policy, attentional instruments, epistemic organs, and shadows. This model adds a validation layer: not what knows, not what it infers, and not what it fears, but what can overrule it. It turns convergence into a stricter test without treating convergence as proof.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-every-insight-has-an-appeal-court.md:22:- notes/source-cards/early-buddhism-sn-22-59-anattalakkhana-sutta.md on aggregates as not fit to be regarded as self.
