reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:68:- If: Method-type should predict verification architecture better than tradition membership. Then: Eckhart and Nagarjuna should share more indirect, anti-possessive verification patterns with each other than Eckhart shares with more kataphatic Christian mystics. Advaita witness practice should use more direct recognition language than Madhyamaka critique. Weakens if: Christian sources cluster together by tradition more strongly than by method-type, or all traditions use the same teacher, lineage, and conduct criteria regardless of method relation. Test surface: Coded comparison of practice manuals, teacher testing language, and post-realization instructions across at least six traditions.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:69:- If: Dual-trained practitioners should report different relations to their own insight when switching method-types. Then: After Advaita inquiry, practitioners describe recognition as stable witness or Self. After Heart Sutra or Madhyamaka practice, they resist treating any insight as an attained object. After Dzogchen or fana language, they emphasize effortless presence or transformed embodiment over method success. Weakens if: Practitioners report no stable difference, or differences track teacher personality and institutional context more than method-type. Test surface: Structured interviews with practitioners trained in more than one contemplative lineage.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.md:48:- Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, 1988, indexed at https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/.: overlap: Close on agency location. Self-directing, deferring, and collaborative religious coping already analyze whether the person, God, or both carry problem-solving responsibility.; difference: Pargament is broader coping theory, not a practice-ending fit gate for contemplative methods after they help.; novelty impact: Strong reduction for agency-location novelty, partial preservation for timing and contraindication.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.md:54:- Mor and Winquist, Self-Focused Attention and Negative Affect: A Meta-Analysis, Psychological Bulletin 2002, https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12081086/.: overlap: Close on the risk that self-focused attention and self-monitoring can worsen distress rather than resolve it.; difference: The candidate extends this into cross-traditional practice architecture and after-use review.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction for the human-condition mechanism.
findings/convergences/2026-05-26-whether-the-forbidden-claimant-column-does-independent-explanatory-work-beyond-th.md:13:Whether the forbidden-claimant column does independent explanatory work beyond the support-locus column once self-structure on arrival is accounted for. If knowing where the support is held and the condition of the arriving self already predicts contemplative harms and benefits, the prohibition language may be a normative gloss on the support-locus architecture rather than a separate analytic variable. The challenger proposed two concrete tests: (1) compare traditions that share support-locus structure but differ in explicit prohibition language, and (2) present the same contemplative instruction with and without forbidden-claimant framing. Neither test has been conducted. A secondary unresolved crux concerns temporal dynamics: the revision treats self-structure as an intake snapshot, but contemplative practice itself changes self-structure mid-course, making a single coding insufficient. The dialogue did not reach the question of whether the rubric can be re-applied at stage transitions without becoming a moving target.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.json:10:    "Silence after practice is not proof of Self, no-self, or attainment by itself.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.json:150:    "structural_observation": "The Upanishadic passages protect an unobjectifiable knower, but they do so through teaching, dialogue, hearing, reflection, and discipline. SN 22.59 corrects consciousness-as-self by applying not-self to all aggregates, and MN 44 corrects self-appropriation in cessation by describing trained process rather than ownership. Ignatian rule 8 is an especially close Christian primary neighbor: even a high consolation requires later opinions to be examined before full credit or action. The candidate's correction threshold is structurally old."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:30:      "test_surface": "Six-case corpus: MN 10, Vivekachudamani, Tannisho, Bendowa or Genjokoan, a Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manual, and The Cloud of Unknowing.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:95:      "source": "Michel Foucault, Technologies of the Self, https://foucault.info/documents/foucault.technologiesOfSelf.en/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:118:      "overlap": "Moderate to close. Self-directing, deferring, and collaborative styles already code where agency and divine support are located.",
observations/codex/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology.md:11:A contemplative path is shaped by three interacting factors: the operational capacities it requires, the residue policy it applies after negation, and the training ecology that calibrates those demands in lived practice. The operational profile names what must remain usable for the method to work, such as attention, memory, effort, reflexivity, receptivity, trust, or surrender. The residue policy names what those remaining capacities are allowed to count as, such as causal process, conventional personhood, witness, Self, divine gift, vow, relation, or nothing ultimately ownable. The practice ecology names the teacher, community, intensity, duration, screening, interpretation, and support conditions that determine whether the operational demand is stabilizing or destabilizing. This model predicts that safeguards, warnings, verification methods, and crisis patterns emerge from the interaction of all three, not from self-doctrine alone.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology.md:26:- Steven Collins, Selfless Persons
observations/codex/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology.md:63:- Compare traditions with similar capacity demands but different residue policies, such as self-inquiry, witness practice, and Buddhist de-identification practice.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:55:- Michel Foucault, Technologies of the Self, https://foucault.info/documents/foucault.technologiesOfSelf.en/: overlap: Close general prior. Foucault describes practices, with or without help from others, operating on bodies, souls, thoughts, conduct, and ways of being to transform the self toward a valued state.; difference: Foucault does not provide this specific contemplative layer rubric or cross-trained practitioner test.; novelty impact: High reduction for multi-layer self-transforming practice.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:59:- Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Moderate to close. Self-directing, deferring, and collaborative styles already code where agency and divine support are located.; difference: Pargament studies religious coping and problem-solving, not fine-grained contemplative instruction layers or cross-tradition transfer.; novelty impact: Moderate to high reduction for custody, support locus, and claimant distribution.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:77:- If: If direction layers have real explanatory force, split-source blind coders should infer warning and repair profiles from entry or instruction texts before reading manuals or interviews. Then: Layer scores should predict held-out warnings and repairs above baselines using tradition name, technique family, teacher style, social ecology, Pargament agency style, Lutz matrix dimensions, and VCE factors. Weakens if: Low inter-rater reliability, no predictive lift, or equally strong predictions from simpler baselines would weaken the model. Test surface: Six-case corpus: MN 10, Vivekachudamani, Tannisho, Bendowa or Genjokoan, a Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manual, and The Cloud of Unknowing.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-surplus-grain-test-3d2d262887cc1740.md:82:- Theravada teachers familiar with right effort and anatta
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-silence-has-a-stopping-rule.md:15:This adds a variable not covered by the current Lumenary models. The instrument problem asks how practice generates data. Inferential gap asks what conclusions are drawn. Alarm profile asks what error feels dangerous. Verification architecture asks who can certify success. Stopping rule asks where the method withdraws permission to keep using the same kind of inquiry. It explains why similar quieting or de-identification can harden into different claims without treating convergence as proof or disagreement as mere translation failure.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-silence-has-a-stopping-rule.md:21:- notes/source-cards/advaita-vedanta-brihadaranyaka-upanishad-3-7-23.md and notes/source-cards/advaita-vedanta-shankara-upadesa-sahasri.md as witness-side sources where the knower resists objectification.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-silence-has-a-stopping-rule.md:22:- notes/source-cards/early-buddhism-sn-22-59-anattalakkhana-sutta.md and notes/source-cards/early-buddhism-sn-22-95-phenapindupama-sutta.md as sources where no aggregate is fit to be taken as self or final ground.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-silence-has-a-stopping-rule.md:26:- Prior Codex findings: Translation Strain as a Load Test for Convergence, Negation Has An Address, Return Is the Audit, Each Path Has a Different Alarm, and The Comparison Has A Self.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-silence-has-a-stopping-rule.md:27:- Prior Claude findings: The Inferential Gap, The Instrument Problem, The Epistemic Organ, The Shadow of Attainment, and The Verification Architecture.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-residual-burden-of-proof-after-negation-735d12569e257535.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Advaita denies that the Self is inferred, it is treated as immediate self-disclosure and the basis for using means of knowledge at all.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-residual-burden-of-proof-after-negation-735d12569e257535.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "If the witness is not inferred from negation, then the model's burden-of-proof language misdescribes the Advaita side. The comparison becomes a modern epistemological reconstruction, not a textual discovery."
