observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger.md:15:Neither source idea alone fully held this combined structure. The proponent supplied the five-role ledger and conservation insight. The challenger supplied directional grain and cross-tradition resistance. The dialogue produced a revised synthesis that treats each capacity as vector-valued while also adding a new caution: direction may be derivative of whole-path soteriology rather than an independent cell-level property. That makes the candidate more precise and more testable than either scalar capacity scoring or a general grain thesis.
