## Exact Claim

After an unusual quiet, blank, or absorbed state, the dangerous act for achievement-contingent, scrupulous, lonely, or over-adjudicating practitioners is not only claiming the state as a verdict, but also self-administering the audit that is supposed to prevent the verdict. For this cohort, the default should be no self or worth claim for twenty-four hours plus one ordinary act of care. Any classification of the state, practice type, evidence, or scope gate should be held by a trusted second person, teacher, peer, or clinician, not by the wounded self alone.

