# Perfectionism Is Increasing Over Time

Source ID: modern-human-condition-curran-hill-perfectionism-increasing
Tradition: modern-human-condition
Type: paper
Path: 
URL: https://doi.org/10.1037/bul0000138

## Notes

Curran and Hill meta-analysis on birth cohort changes in perfectionism from 1989 to 2016. Use as grounding for achievement pressure, socially prescribed perfectionism, performance-based self-worth, comparison, shame, and why result-release practices are targeted remedies rather than universal practices.

